	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>N Orls</placeName> <date>Apl 13. 5608</date></p>
				<p>My dear friend</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">A few days since I found at <persName>Mr Steels</persName> the<lb/> Prayer books for <persName>Mr Andrews</persName>&#44; took them &#38; sent them to her.  Yester<lb/>day I asked <persName>Mr Andrews</persName> for the amt due for them &#36;30&#44; which<lb/> he has paid&#44; but as I could find no <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName> Bank<lb/> notes at the Brokers Offices&#44; I had to pay Banker 1 &#189; &#37;<lb/> premium for the enclosed.  Please acknowledge<lb/> receipt of this &#38; my last letter in which I sent<lb/> &#36;10. &#38; let me know if this kind of remittance<lb/> is satisfactory.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Since I lately addressed you I have been<lb/> very much bothered with my own business &#38; with setting<lb/> estimates for finishing the inside of the synagogue<lb/> after I had closed one contract <persName>Mr Touro</persName> yielded to<lb/> certain alterations in the building which I wanted&#44; &#38; he<lb/> kicked at till I had decided to give them up.  I am<lb/> worried half to death by the members of the congregation on<lb/> the one hand &#38; mechanics <add>&#63;</add> on the other&#44; a perfect scape<lb/>goat to bear the sins of all.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Business generally here is at a stand &#38; no money<lb/> to be had however much may be due to one.  I hope however<lb/> that better times are coming&#44; but so far as I am concerned<lb/> the summer is a severe ordeal for a newspaper.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I trust the French Revolution will lend to the enlargement<lb/> of the power of <placeName>Israel</placeName> throughout the world.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Excuse the brevity of this my dear friend &#38; pity a poor devil<lb/> like me whose entire life has been a struggle&#44; whose every relation<lb/> in life is so encumbered with stumbling blocks&#44; that I would cheerfully<lb/> quit this for another &#38; I trust a better world.  Believe me sincerely your friend</p>
			<p rend="indent(8)">in haste <persName role="author">G. Kursheedt</persName></p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p><addressee>Revd. Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)"><placeName>Penna.</placeName></p>
		</body>
